name: Brown Wax Canvas Native Tote Bag
description:
The body of this tote bag is made with brown waxed canvas and cotton print with a native print in blown/black and gold highlights, lined with cream cotton fabric. The leather straps are 26" and there are two rings in the interior for an adjustable shoulder strap. 

On the inside, there is a magnetic closure. This bag would be great for a weekend getaway, shopping, farmers markets and daily use.

You will find four pockets on the interior, 4" x 4.5"

Measurements:
17" x 11" x 5" 
26" leather straps
53" strap when not adjusted

The waxed canvas is soft to the touch and durable, absolutely gorgeous fabric. WIth each use, the waxed canvas adds more and more character to your satchel.

Ships priority mail within the US.

Do not machine wash wax canvas or leather.
